description:
As a tester 
I would like to have smoketest
So I can test the basic functionality of the app

elements.name: ELT-10 verify Active user is Able to Login

steps.name: I should not see native keyboard
I should not see native keyboard
I should see "Fluke Terms of Service and Privacy Policy"

arguments.val: Fluke Terms of Service and Privacy Policy

elements.name: ELT-252 verify user can Add Manual measurement

steps.name: I wait and press "Add manual measurement"
I type and remember random manual measurement
I wait up to 60 seconds for done syncing
I do a fast sign in as "autotech@org1auto.com"
I wait up to 60 seconds for done loading "History"
I wait and press "Permanently delete measurement?"

elements.name: ELT-254 Verify user can Capture Measurement from module

steps.name: I check to have 1 connected module
I wait for "CAPTURE" button to become enabled
I check display mode to be "Numeric"
I wait up to 60 seconds for done syncing
I do a fast sign in as "autotech@org1auto.com"
I wait up to 60 seconds for done loading "History"
I wait to see saved text note
I wait to see 1 voice note
I wait and press "Permanently delete measurement?"

elements.name: ELT-243 verify user can Capture Measurement by Recording

steps.name: I check to have 1 connected modules
I wait for "CAPTURE" button to become enabled

I wait up to 60 seconds for done syncing
I do a fast sign in as "autotech@org1auto.com"
I wait up to 60 seconds for done loading "History"
I check display mode to be "Graph"
I wait and press "Permanently delete measurement?"

elements.name: ELT-630 Verify user can Capture multiple measurements by Recording

steps.name: I check to have 3 connected modules
I wait for "3-Phase Monitoring" to pop up and I tap "No"
I check display mode to be "Graph"
I wait up to 60 seconds for done syncing
I do a fast sign in as "autotech@org1auto.com"
I wait up to 60 seconds for done loading "History"

elements.name: ELT-104 Verify measurement Added to Work Order can be seen by Team Member

steps.name: I wait to see "New Work Order" title
I wait and press "Work Order Number"
I type and remember random work order number
I enter "ELT-104" into the "workOrderTitle" input field
I wait up to 60 seconds for done syncing
I type saved work order number
I wait and press "Work Order Number"
I wait up to 60 seconds for done loading "History"
I should see an attached measurement
I wait up to 60 seconds for done syncing
I type saved work order number
I wait and press "Work Order Number"
I wait to see saved screen title
I should see an attached measurement

elements.name: ELT-103 Verify Single measurement Added to Equipment can be Seen by Team Member

steps.name: I type and remember random equipment name
I wait and press "Create New Measurement"
I type and remember random manual measurement
I wait up to 60 seconds for done syncing

elements.name: ELT-77 Validate user is able to add work order with All Fields entered and Marked Completed

steps.name: I wait to see "New Work Order" title
I wait to see "Work Order Number"
I wait to see "Work Order Title"
I wait to see "Mark as Completed"
I wait and press "Work Order Number"
I type and remember random work order number
I wait to see 1 voice note
I wait up to 60 seconds for done syncing
I do a fast sign in as "autotech@org1auto.com"
I type saved work order number
I wait and press "Work Order Number"
I wait to see saved screen title
I check date and time for "Unplanned" work order which is marked as "Completed"
I wait to see "Testing with Calabash"
I wait to see "Voice and Text Notes"
I wait to see 1 voice note
